longBusinessSummary: Koios Beverage Corp., together with its subsidiaries, produces, markets, and sells functional beverages in the United States. The company also provides supplements and coffee products. It distributes its products through a network of approximately 4,400 retail locations and Website. The company was formerly known as Super Nova Petroleum Corp. and changed its name to Koios Beverage Corp. in April 2018. Koios Beverage Corp. was incorporated in 2012 and is headquartered in Denver, Colorado.
